---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="How AdBunny's AI Banner Optimization Works"
  description="See exactly how AdBunny's single JS tag and AI optimization layer turn remnant ad inventory into revenue, step by step."
  keywords="how AI banner optimization works, ad tag integration, real-time banner optimization, ad monetization process"
>

<section class="min-h-[70vh] flex items-center" style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)">
  <div class="max-w-[80rem] mx-auto px-8 py-32 max-md:py-20 w-full">
    <p class="kicker mb-8">How It Works</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif leading-[1.08] tracking-tight mb-6" style="font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem);font-weight:550">from empty ad slot to optimized revenue</h1>
    <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color:var(--color-text-secondary)">Four steps. One tag. Zero engineering lift.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Step 01 -->
<section class="py-28 max-md:py-16" style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)">
  <div class="max-w-[80rem] mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center max-md:grid-cols-1 max-md:gap-12">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-5 mb-8">
          <span class="font-serif text-sm" style="color:var(--color-text-tertiary)">01</span>
          <p class="kicker">Add the tag</p>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-serif leading-[1.08] tracking-tight mb-6" style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:550">paste a single JavaScript snippet</h2>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed max-w-[28rem]" style="color:var(--color-text-secondary)">No SDK, no server integration, no waterfall configuration. Just one tag into the pages or slots you want AdBunny to cover.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="/images/step1-tag-glow.png" alt="Adding the AdBunny tag to your page" class="w-full" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Step 02 -->
<section class="py-28 max-md:py-16" style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)">
  <div class="max-w-[80rem] mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center max-md:grid-cols-1 max-md:gap-12">
      <div class="max-md:order-2">
        <img src="/images/step2-evaluate-glow.png" alt="AdBunny evaluating available demand" class="w-full" />
      </div>
      <div class="max-md:order-1">
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-5 mb-8">
          <span class="font-serif text-sm" style="color:var(--color-text-tertiary)">02</span>
          <p class="kicker">Evaluate demand</p>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-serif leading-[1.08] tracking-tight mb-6" style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:550">AdBunny evaluates available demand</h2>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed max-w-[28rem]" style="color:var(--color-text-secondary)">When a covered slot loads, AdBunny's optimization layer evaluates the banner demand available for that specific impression in real time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Step 03 -->
<section class="py-28 max-md:py-16" style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)">
  <div class="max-w-[80rem] mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center max-md:grid-cols-1 max-md:gap-12">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-5 mb-8">
          <span class="font-serif text-sm" style="color:var(--color-text-tertiary)">03</span>
          <p class="kicker">AI selects the best</p>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-serif leading-[1.08] tracking-tight mb-6" style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:550">the AI picks the best-paying banner</h2>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed max-w-[28rem]" style="color:var(--color-text-secondary)">Rather than following a fixed, static call order, the system picks whichever available banner is likely to generate the most revenue for that impression, right now.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="/images/step3-ai-glow.png" alt="AI selecting the best-paying banner" class="w-full" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Step 04 -->
<section class="py-28 max-md:py-16" style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)">
  <div class="max-w-[80rem] mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center max-md:grid-cols-1 max-md:gap-12">
      <div class="max-md:order-2">
        <img src="/images/metaphor-hourglass-glow.png" alt="Revenue flowing from filled impressions" class="w-full" />
      </div>
      <div class="max-md:order-1">
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-5 mb-8">
          <span class="font-serif text-sm" style="color:var(--color-text-tertiary)">04</span>
          <p class="kicker">Get paid</p>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-serif leading-[1.08] tracking-tight mb-6" style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:550">the slot fills, you get paid</h2>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed max-w-[28rem]" style="color:var(--color-text-secondary)">The impression fills, and revenue starts flowing from inventory that used to sit empty or monetize at low, static rates.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- What you don't have to do -->
<section class="py-32 max-md:py-20" style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)">
  <div class="max-w-[80rem] mx-auto px-8">
    <p class="kicker mb-12">What you don't have to do</p>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 max-w-[36rem]">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <span class="split-check"></span>
        <span class="text-base" style="color:var(--color-text-secondary)">No waterfall to build or maintain</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <span class="split-check"></span>
        <span class="text-base" style="color:var(--color-text-secondary)">No line items to configure</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <span class="split-check"></span>
        <span class="text-base" style="color:var(--color-text-secondary)">No manual optimization or A/B testing of network order</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <span class="split-check"></span>
        <span class="text-base" style="color:var(--color-text-secondary)">No conflict with your existing primary demand</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="py-32 max-md:py-20 text-center">
  <div class="max-w-[80rem] mx-auto px-8">
    <h2 class="font-serif leading-[1.08] tracking-tight mb-6" style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:550">see it running on your own inventory</h2>
    <p class="text-base mb-10" style="color:var(--color-text-secondary)">One tag. Four steps. Revenue from inventory that used to sit empty.</p>
    <a href="/get-started" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get Your JS Tag</a>
  </div>
</section>
